- cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) is also likely as the paper involves combinatorial analysis and proof techniques.
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is another possible category as the paper deals with the complexity of regular languages under different operations.
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is a potential category as the paper involves boolean operations, which are closely related to logic.
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper may involve some information-theoretic concepts in the analysis of regular languages.
